Dear Mr. Adam,

When combined with data analytics, this powerful tool can help you to identify new leads, save you time on your marketing efforts, and target the right people, with the right products, at the right time.

There is, however, a distinction to be made between the type of automation being used. There are three primary kinds of email automation: automatic email responses, email automations, and auto-generated emails. Below, we’ll explore the differences between the three, and we’ll show you how to start saving time and effort in creating your own messages.


Best Regards, 
        
Adam Stanler
Customer Service Manager
BrainNet Fiber
London
